00:24:53,800 --> 00:24:56,840
 Such a different posturing than Mary sitting

567
00:24:56,840 --> 00:25:00,240
 at the feet of Christ, that she's so distracted

568
00:25:00,240 --> 00:25:02,120
 that she gets caught up in the self-centeredness.

569
00:25:02,120 --> 00:25:05,300
 Again, I believe wanting the approval of others

570
00:25:05,300 --> 00:25:08,640
 that in a moment she thinks that she can tell God,

571
00:25:08,640 --> 00:25:11,560
 the one who formed her in her mother's womb, what to do.

