00:25:27,320 --> 00:25:29,120
 And maybe you don't say that out loud,

581
00:25:29,120 --> 00:25:31,080
 but maybe that's the cry of your heart.

582
00:25:31,080 --> 00:25:35,280
 And it's time to sit still.

583
00:25:35,280 --> 00:25:41,340
 In the servant's position at the feet of the Lord Almighty.

584
00:25:41,340 --> 00:25:43,840
 Saying, I can't, but you can.

