00:25:56,920 --> 00:25:59,800
 The highest levels of anxiety

591
00:25:59,800 --> 00:26:02,920
 the world as we know it have ever seen.

592
00:26:02,920 --> 00:26:06,280
 And it starts with this idea

593
00:26:06,280 --> 00:26:08,320
 that we think we control things.

594
00:26:08,320 --> 00:26:09,840
 We don't control things.

595
00:26:09,840 --> 00:26:11,640
 God controls things.

596
00:26:11,640 --> 00:26:13,400
 So you'd be better off spending time

597
00:26:13,400 --> 00:26:15,700
 with the one who controls everything.

598
00:26:15,700 --> 00:26:18,480
 Martha's anxious, it says.

